## Exemplos de uso

Uso do pacote como biblioteca, fora do pipeline:

```python
from risk_models import (
    DataSource, download_market_data, log_returns,
    historical_var, conditional_var, fit_garch,
)

md = download_market_data(("PETR4.SA", "VALE3.SA"), start="2022-01-02",
                          source=DataSource.AUTO)
rets = log_returns(md.prices)

var99 = historical_var(rets["PETR4.SA"], alpha=0.99)   # ex.: 0.041 => 4,1%
es99 = conditional_var(rets["PETR4.SA"], alpha=0.99)   # sempre >= var99

g = fit_garch(rets["PETR4.SA"])
print(f"VaR 99%: {var99:.2%} | CVaR: {es99:.2%} | "
      f"vol prevista (anual): {g.forecast_vol_annual:.1%} | "
      f"persistência: {g.persistence:.3f}")
```

